\n而家香港自殺個案飆升，好早期天水圍已經因為自殺事件而被稱為「悲情城市」，之後呃綜緩，假結婚，走水貨，全部都係主流媒體未大肆報導前，我地已經經歷曬，好早就對大陸人有敵意，所以點解元朗光復🐶多人，點解咁多人投本土。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"根本最多出黎鳩嗡班廢老唔係住深水埗就係觀塘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"仲有黃大仙＋慈雲山"},{"pid":"9314c16e16d369de2b795f604b201c034a483618","tid":1269540,"uid":79828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"03d4d421589902a3b8238946c75663a69653ea93","tid":1269540,"uid":263261,"like":96,"dislike":5,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"教育 通識科<br />\n天水圍仲有好多好老師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"83d6c3c0f383060c6e3cc7629a89b47fc4724023","tid":1269540,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c464cdfb0650f79e3c2233ce4f9687c4b89e4c28","tid":1269540,"uid":237947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"595a571a5f7c742d4dd0b1629cf2f27d4bf62694","tid":1269540,"uid":227275,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"點解新移民就唔可以係本土派票倉"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"8 何君堯 35,657 當選<br />\n<br />\n12 李卓人 30,149<br />\n11 黃浩銘 28,529<br />\n1 黃潤達 20,974<br />\n15 馮檢基 17,872<br />\n<br />\n就係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"成班on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcb96ce2d1ea0da147f19331cc7559e52eb5a14","tid":1269540,"uid":267718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c3a30e6aa38d393ef3b7d260025e30abfcda87b","tid":1269540,"uid":63303,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"證明仔女同父母嘅政治傾向係可以唔同<br />\n無論嚟自邊度嘅移民，後代自幼接受香港教育，擁抱香港文化，都可以成為香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"呢個一直以黎都係我地香港人嘅精神。無論乜野人。都可以係香港人。好似包致金法官咁。唔通你話渠唔係香港人咩。"},{"pid":"89c9e4b80add6611b6de74ebb7d46ab926d06f27","tid":1269540,"uid":245126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"